%F A395324 Equals sqrt(2 - 2*sqrt((2*sqrt(5) + 5)/15)).
%F A395324 Minimal polynomial: 45*x^8 - 360*x^6 + 960*x^4 - 960*x^2 + 256. - _Stefano Spezia_, Apr 21 2026
